{"word":"Στύξ","slug":"Στύξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n97397\" key=\"*stu/c\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Στύξ</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, gen. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Στῠγός, </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">στυγέω</etym>) <sense id=\"n97397.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the Styx</tr_>, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the Hateful</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:369\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.369</biblScope> </bibl>: also the nymph of this river, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:361\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">361</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n97397.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a well of fatal coldness in Arcadia</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:74\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.74</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:8:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.8.4</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:18:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.18.5</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n97397.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as Appellat., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">monster, reptile</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄτρωτον . . ὑπὸ στυγός </foreign>(<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στύγος</foreign> cod.M) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:532\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ch.\">Ch.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">532</biblScope> </bibl> (sed leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στύγους</foreign>). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n97397.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">piercing chill, as of frost</tr_>, in pl., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αἱ στύγες εἰσδύονται εἰς τὰ σώματα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:5:14:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CP\">CP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.14.4</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n97397.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hatred, abhorrence</tr_>, esp. of mankind, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0640.tlg001:3:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alciphr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.34</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n97397.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">σκώψ</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0651.tlg001:21:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.Lib.\">Ant.Lib.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.5</biblScope></bibl>, Hygin. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fab.\">Fab.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">28.4</biblScope> </bibl> Rose, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>: cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στρίξ</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}